-- Eastern Plaguelands
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Welcome to Light\'s Hope Chapel.\r\n\r\nYou wish to join the Crusade?  Very well.  We have plenty of tasks for new recruits.\r\n\r\nBut first, a test. ' WHERE  `entry`=27463;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I see them!  Can you?  The little pig spirits, on their way to the great sty in the sky...' WHERE  `entry`=27533;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Why, this is exactly what I needed!  Fine, I\'ll forgive Tarenar for running off.\r\n\r\n$N, you\'re welcome to join us anytime.', `RequestItemsText`='I should have guessed it.  Tarenar made you get me a gift?  That thoughtless idiot!\r\n\r\nUmm... what was the gift, anyhow?' WHERE  `entry`=27372;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='What is this?  A warsword?  A butter knife?  I\'m useless when it comes to blades.  Let me see...\r\n\r\nAh!  This sword was once in the hand of a great man, but there is much tragedy in that man\'s past.\r\n\r\nAre you here to help him?  It\'s far too late for him now... but perhaps we can help him in the past!', `RequestItemsText`='There is something timely about your visit.  You\'re not from the future, are you?' WHERE  `entry`=27386;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='May my pile never stop growing.', `RequestItemsText`='You seem to have your hands full.  Are those skulls I see?' WHERE  `entry`=27539;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Even if the flowers died out shortly after they bloomed, they proved our point to the Scourge: they are losing, and we are winning.\r\n\r\nThank you for your assistance.' WHERE  `entry`=27421;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You brought us a shaman!  From the Earthen Ring, no less!\r\n\r\nI have no idea how we\'ll fit him in the caravan, but we\'ll find a way.  Welcome aboard, Rimblat Earthshatter!' WHERE  `entry`=27457;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Hello, $N!  Glad to see you\'ve rejoined the caravan!\r\n\r\nTarenar and Gidwin arrived here before you.  Tarenar\'s just right there, and Gidwin\'s... well... he\'s in a little bit of a mood right now.  I think he\'s in the tower.' WHERE  `entry`=27466;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'ve returned sooner than I expected.  Excellent.\r\n\r\nWe will continue our path into the north.  Next, you will be completing a similar task - this time, in Northdale.' WHERE  `entry`=27465;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Remember that your ancestors always watch over you.  As a brother of the Argent Crusade, you will join a family that has a long line of such fallen ancestors.  Their vigil and protection will be your strength as you press forward against the Scourge.\r\n\r\nCongratulations Tarenar, Gidwin, and $N.  Welcome to the Argent Crusade.' WHERE  `entry`=27464;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It sounds like Korfax really cleaned house over at the barracks.  It\'s very much like him to show off like that.' WHERE  `entry`=27618;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You see a trail-worn journal inside the caravan.  Judging by the Argent Crusade emblem on its spine, it must belong to Argus.\r\n\r\nWritten within the journal are several accounts of Argus\' experiences during his tenure in the Crusade.  It should prove to be an interesting read while on the road.' WHERE  `entry`=27560;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='There it is!  And oh my!  I forgot how full it was!\r\n\r\nThis is a glorious day, $N!  Stupendous!  Insanely good, I say!', `RequestItemsText`='Do you have my receipt book?  I can\'t wait to get back to business!' WHERE  `entry`=27534;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It sounds like you were successful.  Hopefully this is enough information to find Gidwin.' WHERE  `entry`=27522;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It looks like Beezil has already made himself comfortable, and has stuffed several peculiar gizmos into the caravan.\r\n\r\nMost of them seem too impractical or dangerous to take with you.  One small cogwheel, however, looks to be fairly well-crafted.' WHERE  `entry`=27562;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Good, the abbey is ours.  I never doubted Eligor\'s ability for a moment.' WHERE  `entry`=27617;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I haven\'t found anything but brainless undead, and plenty of them.  I was just about to kill my way into Stratholme when you arrived.\r\n\r\nDid you have any more success?' WHERE  `entry`=27524;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I can\'t believe it.  We\'re literally FEET away from becoming sworn members of the Argent Crusade.\r\n\r\nWe\'d be in there already if it weren\'t for Tarenar\'s dallying.  If he doesn\'t quit chatting with the locals soon, I\'m going to head in there myself.' WHERE  `entry`=27455;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Our duty for the day is done.\r\n\r\nIt is only a matter of time before we defeat the Scourge.  Today, we made progress.' WHERE  `entry`=27467;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Uh oh... it looks like we may have gathered a little too much coagulated rot.  Oh well, we\'ll just have to improvise, then!\r\n\r\nWhat could possibly go wrong?', `RequestItemsText`='We\'re nearly ready to strike, $N.' WHERE  `entry`=27453;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I suppose I had better work on my stealth, if you were able to find me.\r\n\r\nAre you interested in helping me heal the Plaguelands?' WHERE  `entry`=27544;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I love the smell of fresh foot scrapings, don\'t you?\r\n\r\nIf we\'re going to find a cure to the plague, we need to get creative with our ingredients.  Now, if you don\'t mind, I\'m going to get back to work.', `RequestItemsText`='You got the stuff?' WHERE  `entry`=27531;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'ve got both pieces!  Good.  These will help when trying to sneak into their death camp.', `RequestItemsText`='Everything going alright so far, $N?' WHERE  `entry`=27452;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It is good to hear you found the tortured souls of my brethren and freed them.  I find my strength renewed, knowing at least some of the defenders of Darrowshire no longer wallow in the vile subservience of the Scourge.' WHERE  `entry`=27529;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent work.  I can now continue my work without the distractions of that great white beast.\r\n\r\nI shall fashion this fur into something you can use.', `RequestItemsText`='I hope you\'ve done away with that creature.' WHERE  `entry`=27523;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Fiona has left some of her charms inside the caravan.\r\n\r\nAs a trader, she seems to be pretty good with money.  Maybe carrying one of her charms will help out with your finances.' WHERE  `entry`=27555;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Hmm... they didn\'t survive the trip out of the water as well as I had hoped.\r\n\r\nOh well!  Seafood salad for Frederick tonight!', `RequestItemsText`='Did... did you bring the fish?' WHERE  `entry`=27450;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='May the Earthmother watch over you! Bless you, young one.', `RequestItemsText`='You will grow to tolerate the taste, $R.  I did.' WHERE  `entry`=27456;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Tarenar?  Is that you?\r\n\r\nWhoever you are, would you mind helping me out of this thing?' WHERE  `entry`=27367;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have no idea how happy I am to see you two!  You\'re a sight for sore eyes... sore eyes that have been starin\' through a banshee for far too long now.\r\n\r\nI\'m sorry for causing so much trouble.  Will you take me back to the caravan?' WHERE  `entry`=27526;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Gidwin has left several bottles of weapon oil inside the caravan.\r\n\r\nHe seems to be quite a fierce combatant up close.  Perhaps his weapon oil will help you out as well.' WHERE  `entry`=27556;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I\'ll tear that pint-size paladin to shreds before he... wait a minute are those Banshee\'s Bells?  You brought these for me?\r\n\r\nOh, Gidwin asked you to get them for me!  That sweet little guy.  Alright.  He\'s off the hook for now.', `RequestItemsText`='Giddy\'s got you mixed up in all of this now?' WHERE  `entry`=27369;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='We\'ve got to keep moving!  We\'re getting so very close!' WHERE  `entry`=27525;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Perhaps you can help, $C.' WHERE  `entry`=28578;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have the relics?  Good.  I will get to work on resolving any temporal discontinuities.\r\n\r\nDon\'t worry... that\'s not something you have to worry about.  You just gather the reagents.', `RequestItemsText`='Do you have the relics, $N?' WHERE  `entry`=27388;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The key fits the lock, and the chest opens...', `RequestItemsText`='This chest is old and covered in grime.' WHERE  `entry`=27391;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes, you are indeed strong... and I submit to you.\r\n\r\nI will join you and your friend, the worgen.  My strength is yours.' WHERE  `entry`=27449;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='That\'s my daddy\'s sword!  How did you find it?  Did you find the bad hunter?', `RequestItemsText`='Daddy loved his animal sword.  He seemed sad when he didn\'t have it anymore.' WHERE  `entry`=27392;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You didn\'t see him?  Where could he have gone then?\r\n\r\nHis... his prayer book?  Why would he leave that behind?\r\n\r\nOh...\r\n\r\nBy the Light, what have I done?', `RequestItemsText`='Northdale is home to a few ghosts and banshees.  Nothing ol\' Giddy can\'t handle.' WHERE  `entry`=27488;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes?' WHERE  `entry`=27683;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I couldn\'t stop him.  While you and Tarenar were out, Giddy ran north all alone!\r\n\r\nTarenar, you should have known better!  Gidwin gets so impatient sometimes, and you only egg him on.  If Giddy gets into any trouble, I\'m blaming you for this.' WHERE  `entry`=27487;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'ve been more help than anyone expected of you, $N.  The doors of my caravan are always open to you.\r\n\r\nThe boys and I have even put together a little something special for you.  Here, take your pick!' WHERE  `entry`=27527;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'re back?!  Thank the Light!\r\n\r\nBefore you throw that acid on me, I need to ask: Are you the guy who was here before, or are you one of those eight-legged cowards?  I need to know whether or not I should smack you on my way out.', `RequestItemsText`='Oh boy... Fiona is going to be madder than a wet harpy.  You\'d better hurry.' WHERE  `entry`=27368;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='It should take them weeks to get their operation running again.  Thank you, $N.' WHERE  `entry`=27454;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'ve come to the right place, mister!  No place better than Terrordale, yes siree, that\'s right!  The jewel of Lordaeron!' WHERE  `entry`=27535;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='While I can\'t agree with their methods, I can\'t argue with their results.  In many ways, the Scarlet were well-intentioned, but their zeal grew too strong, and their hate blinded them to reason.\r\n\r\nI only hope that the same doesn\'t happen to our Brotherhood of Light.' WHERE  `entry`=27620;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Hello.  I\'m Pamela, what\'s your name?' WHERE  `entry`=27383;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent work, $N.  Are you certain you haven\'t done this before?', `RequestItemsText`='Do you have the skulls?  They are critical for my spell, which will give us the chance to save Darrowshire.  Maybe.' WHERE  `entry`=27389;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Time is wasting, $N.  Every minute we waste gives the Scourge another chance to kill Gidwin.  If he isn\'t dead already.\r\n\r\nNot that I think he is.  Giddy may be a stick-in-the-mud, but when it comes down to it, he can swing the Light like a champion.' WHERE  `entry`=27489;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Hope the ride wasn\'t too bumpy for you.\r\n\r\nHave a look around the tower while the horses rest.  It\'s no Light\'s Hope Chapel, but I\'m sure you can find some way to keep yourself busy.' WHERE  `entry`=27373;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='My duty is not over yet.  In many ways, this was the easy step.', `RequestItemsText`='I have waited long for this day.' WHERE  `entry`=27481;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You see a small doll sitting in the back corner of the caravan.\r\n\r\nTarenar tells you that it must belong to Gidwin, and Gidwin says that it\'s probably Tarenar\'s.' WHERE  `entry`=27558;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You found it!  You found my doll!  Oh, thank you!', `RequestItemsText`='Did you find my doll?' WHERE  `entry`=27384;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The sooner those Scourge are pushed out of the Fungal Vale, the sooner we can heal it.\r\n\r\nThank you, $N.' WHERE  `entry`=27420;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Oh, hallelujah, and praise, praise be to the Light, my brother!', `RequestItemsText`='<Deacon Andaal is deep in prayer.>' WHERE  `entry`=27479;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You notice a small heap of stones within the caravan.\r\n\r\nThey do not appear out-of-the-ordinary, yet one of them attracts your attention.  You sense a warmth coming from within it.' WHERE  `entry`=27561;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Of course a young $R like you would have no trouble taking care of a few wild animals.  With the roads clear, my journey to the next tower will be much easier.' WHERE  `entry`=27382;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Well done, $N.  I will deliver these to Tyrosus when we return.', `RequestItemsText`='I hope you gave them a fight.' WHERE  `entry`=27614;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='A blessed fire cleanses even the most corrupt of flesh.\r\n\r\nThey stood no chance in the face of the Light.' WHERE  `entry`=27528;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Well well well!  Someone who goes and gets things done!  Here\'s your cut, chief.  I\'ll be seein\' you around.', `RequestItemsText`='You\'ve been fightin\' undead.  Did ya find Browman?' WHERE  `entry`=27458;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The flare is fully assembled, and the matches lie unused next to the fuse.\r\n\r\nThe fallen Argent centurion got much closer to setting off this flare than you had guessed.' WHERE  `entry`=27460;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I\'ve found them, $R.  The Scourge.  How I\'ve longed for this day.' WHERE  `entry`=27370;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Tarenar has laid a few holy talismans inside the caravan.  They appear to be unused.\r\n\r\nThey appear to be magical in nature.  If Tarenar isn\'t using them, what\'s the harm in borrowing one for a while?' WHERE  `entry`=27557;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The death of Rohan eases my spirits a bit.\r\n\r\nI once fought beside him, you know.  He was an emissary of the Scarlet Crusade; one of the few that deigned to join us in our battle against Kel\'thuzad, so many years ago.  How quickly things change.' WHERE  `entry`=27613;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This is it!  If this missive is to be believed, then he\'s literally right over this hill!\r\n\r\nWhat are we waiting for, $N?', `RequestItemsText`='What?  Did you find something?' WHERE  `entry`=27551;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The fighting is over!  I heard my daddy whisper to me.  He scared away all the ghosts and he says he\'s coming home!  I\'m so happy!\r\n\r\nHe also said I should welcome you if came to our house, so I made some tea!\r\n\r\nI hope you like lots of sugar!' WHERE  `entry`=27390;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='A $C!  Just what we needed.  Your arrival couldn\'t have been more timely.' WHERE  `entry`=27459;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Good, good.  These barracks are as good as fallen.' WHERE  `entry`=27619;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You are a true Champion of the Light, $N.  I wish you luck in your future endeavors, wherever they might take you.\r\n\r\nIf you need anything in the future, you can always find me here - knee-deep in the corpses of the slain.' WHERE  `entry`=27530;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Keep this up and I may have to keep you here at Eastwall, $R.' WHERE  `entry`=27477;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='One less thing to worry about.  Nice work up there.' WHERE  `entry`=27616;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Whew.  Every time Argus comes plodding through that Plaguewood, I fear it to be his last.  It\'s good to see that he\'s wise enough to send a youngblood like you in his stead.', `RequestItemsText`='Highbeacon\'s Parcel... is Argus safe?  Did something happen?' WHERE  `entry`=27532;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='We\'ve enjoyed having you ride with us, $N.  Hopefully, once Gidwin and Tarenar join the Argent Crusade, we can continue to travel together.' WHERE  `entry`=27448;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You are well on your way to becoming a true champion of the Light, $N.  Well done.' WHERE  `entry`=27615;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Hello!  It\'s me.  Hope you don\'t mind a little home-brewed magic to allow me to communicate with you in the field.  It\'ll save us both some time.\r\n\r\nWe\'re going to incorporate that living rot into a mixture that\'ll ruin their next batch of plague.  That\'ll show them!', `RequestItemsText`='How are things looking in Corin\'s Crossing?' WHERE  `entry`=27451;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Well met, $N.  Can I trust you to assist me in taking this abbey away from these abominations?' WHERE  `entry`=27461;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I\'ll be handling things from here, $C.\r\n\r\nFine, you want an assignment?  I suppose I can afford to send you in on a mission or two.' WHERE  `entry`=27462;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Argus Highbeacon... that old guy on the top of the tower?  Great!\r\n\r\nA man his age must have been in the Argent Crusade for a long time.  Maybe he can put in the good word for us at Light\'s Hope.' WHERE  `entry`=27381;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'ve seen Pamela?  She\'s alive?\r\n\r\nShe\'s dead?  No!  Oh, Pamela!  Why does your spirit still suffer in this world?  Why are you perished, while fortune keeps me alive?  In an instant I would switch places with you and wander dead Darrowshire, a ghost and alone!\r\n\r\nAh, but this news cannot change fate.  Thank you, $N.  Now my duty, my duty to revenge, burns hot as ever.\r\n\r\nSay, what is that sword you have there?', `RequestItemsText`='Any news of my Pammy?' WHERE  `entry`=27385;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Vex\'tul has left some of his wrappings within the caravan.  Surprisingly, he was courteous enough to keep them folded and separate from everyone else\'s belongings.\r\n\r\nVex\'tul values strength over everything else.  Leaning in close, you can sense some of his residual strength emanating from within these armbands.' WHERE  `entry`=27559;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The abbey will fall shortly.  We can soon move on, deeper into Tyr\'s Hand.' WHERE  `entry`=27612;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You found them!  Well done, $N!  These relics hold within them the memories of the Scourge forces at Darrowshire.  We will need these if we are to save your Joseph Redpath.', `RequestItemsText`='Did you find the skull and the sword, $N?' WHERE  `entry`=27387;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes?' WHERE  `entry`=27684;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Perhaps you can help, $C.' WHERE  `entry`=28577;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Five should be good enough.\r\n\r\nYikes, look at the time!  I need to head back to camp.' WHERE  `entry`=27371;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Do not feel sorry for me.  Those were my friends that you saw at Quel\'lithien Lodge, but they were already as good as dead.' WHERE  `entry`=27521;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Great, you got him!  And I hope you taught his gang a lesson too!', `RequestItemsText`='Did you find the hideout, $N?  Did you take care of Zaeldarr?' WHERE  `entry`=27432;